    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "2021 Honda Accord in good condition. The interior shows minor wear consistent with regular use, and the exterior has a few small scuffs but no major damage. Mechanically sound with all systems functioning properly. No accident history and no modifications.",
